  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Effect of Atorvastatin on the Pharmacokinetics of Fimasartan in Healthy Male Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Two-treatment, Two-period, Two-sequence, Crossover Study to Evaluate the Effect of Atorvastatin on the Pharmacokinetics of Fimasartan in Healthy Male Volunteers</official_title>
